{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC03_LIN_070.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x21,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Oh, so what happened with your<CR>friend-making assignment you were<CR>talking about?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Well...my progress stopped after reaching 98 left."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I-I see... Making friends is tough."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "I did not know that hidden behind the sweet ring of \"make friends,\" I would discover such a difficult trial."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Well, I'm sure having lots of friends would be fun, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Even if you don't have many, I'm sure it'll be okay as long as you have a deep connection with the friends you have."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Thank you for cheering me up.<CR>My heart feels lighter now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "So, who's this other person that became your friend?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "It is Marion."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Huh...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Because I was making so little progress, I begged her and gained her approval."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "I see. Hmhmhm, I'm happy for you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Although, Marion had a bit of a wry face..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x36,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "(I guess Marion wanted Linca to make friends with other people...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "But, I am happy that Marion became my friend for some reason."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Well, I think your relationship as friends started way before this."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x41,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Before...? Now that you mention it, maybe..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x165,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "I did not notice it until now, but...we were friends, Marion and I."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x167,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "At this rate, I may be able to make one more friend before the end of the year."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Oh, are you looking for a friend?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Well now, if that's the case,<CR>you should've come to me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Oh, Mr. Harry. Is it okay for you to be away from your job?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "My duty is to lend a helping hand to the troubled people of this town."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x22,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Linca, rejoice. As of today, you and I are friends!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Stranger..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x25,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "No, no, I'm sure you're familiar with my face. I take a good amount of pride in being a bit of a celebrity."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x1a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Now, there's no need to hold back..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x77,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Marion told me not follow strangers."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x78,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "If you come any closer, I will cut you!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x141,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Hey now, calm down! Ayesha, can you talk to her, too?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x142,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "I'm not a stranger! And I'd make a suitable friend for her!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "Linca, let's put that sharp tool away for now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "(Hahaha...hmm, maybe these two being friends...might not be...so...good...)"
        }
    ]
}